com.mcc.ul
Class AoInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.AoInfo

public class AoInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to retrieve information that describe the capabilities of the analog output subsystem on a DAQ device. To create an instance of this class, call the getInfo() method of the AoDevice class.
